  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is \"Your Turn To Die\"?</strong></h2>Your Turn To Die -Death Game By Majority- is a multi-ending horror adventure game. <br>Your decision will directly affect the story and final outcome!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2>Sara Chidouin returns home from school late one night to discover that something's gone terribly wrong.<br>When she comes to, she finds herself, her friend Joe, and 9 other people trapped in a mysterious place.<br>Placed in life-and-death situations, they must come to an agreement about what they should do - and who should die.<br><br><strong>1. Explore and interact with the unique characters and find a way to escape from the enclosed space!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/042732edce769e67cb7ed0528979bbd4.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" width=390 height=624 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/042732edce769e67cb7ed0528979bbd4.webm?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2. Based on the role cards you are given, discuss and determine who to vote for!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/53dba47f71e33dfb38f6ecd231fb6e01.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" width=408 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/53dba47f71e33dfb38f6ecd231fb6e01.webm?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/53dba47f71e33dfb38f6ecd231fb6e01.mp4?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/a0a08987e3d3514a2d1e956c2ca36a30.gif?t=1749009769\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/a0a08987e3d3514a2d1e956c2ca36a30.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br><strong>3. Sometimes, in addition to discussions, they are forced to participate in games of life!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/8ee5b9d40d154b6fcd13085e0d6148cf.apng?t=1749009769\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/8ee5b9d40d154b6fcd13085e0d6148cf.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" class=\"bb_img\" width=580 height=380 /></picture></span><br><br>Your vote will change the fate of the survivors.<br><strong>Save the weak or save the beneficial, the choice is yours.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/ea8e92f747e25b294803ca3e276d4a8c.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/ea8e92f747e25b294803ca3e276d4a8c.webm?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The upcoming Early Access version is not yet complete main story wise; the first part of chapter 3 is complete. The second part will be added as soon as it is completed!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Special Thanks --</strong></h2><i>English Localization: </i><br><strong>vgperson</strong> (Twitter: @KerokeroCoder)",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is \"Your Turn To Die\"?</strong></h2>Your Turn To Die -Death Game By Majority- is a multi-ending horror adventure game. <br>Your decision will directly affect the story and final outcome!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2>Sara Chidouin returns home from school late one night to discover that something's gone terribly wrong.<br>When she comes to, she finds herself, her friend Joe, and 9 other people trapped in a mysterious place.<br>Placed in life-and-death situations, they must come to an agreement about what they should do - and who should die.<br><br><strong>1. Explore and interact with the unique characters and find a way to escape from the enclosed space!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/042732edce769e67cb7ed0528979bbd4.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" width=390 height=624 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/042732edce769e67cb7ed0528979bbd4.webm?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2. Based on the role cards you are given, discuss and determine who to vote for!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/53dba47f71e33dfb38f6ecd231fb6e01.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" width=408 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/53dba47f71e33dfb38f6ecd231fb6e01.webm?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/53dba47f71e33dfb38f6ecd231fb6e01.mp4?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/a0a08987e3d3514a2d1e956c2ca36a30.gif?t=1749009769\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/a0a08987e3d3514a2d1e956c2ca36a30.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br><strong>3. Sometimes, in addition to discussions, they are forced to participate in games of life!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/8ee5b9d40d154b6fcd13085e0d6148cf.apng?t=1749009769\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/8ee5b9d40d154b6fcd13085e0d6148cf.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" class=\"bb_img\" width=580 height=380 /></picture></span><br><br>Your vote will change the fate of the survivors.<br><strong>Save the weak or save the beneficial, the choice is yours.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/ea8e92f747e25b294803ca3e276d4a8c.poster.avif?t=1749009769\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067780/extras/ea8e92f747e25b294803ca3e276d4a8c.webm?t=1749009769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The upcoming Early Access version is not yet complete main story wise; the first part of chapter 3 is complete. The second part will be added as soon as it is completed!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Special Thanks --</strong></h2><i>English Localization: </i><br><strong>vgperson</strong> (Twitter: @KerokeroCoder)",
